乎白痴的程度，剛做的事轉身就忘了，怎麼想也想不起來。腦力不行，學業事業都會一塌糊塗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港戒丁論壇 ：<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=be135a17\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com</a><br />\n中醫爆影響五臟六腑：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_8REr3KZku0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_8REr3KZku0&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8ffb94fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_8REr3KZku0</a><br />\n打丁同做愛既分別：<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com/viewthread.php?tid=2&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D2%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c8abb0a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com/viewthread.php?tid=2&amp;extra=page%3D1</a><br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK專頁：香港戒丁論壇，想入WHATSAPP群就ＰＭ我"},{"pid":"83373802f445e82c5f59aa9581bd06ea2dab1caf","tid":122033,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問下蕭別離就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實邊個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96123de6a066990a0c369b2b6949b1d791ffef23","tid":122033,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問下蕭別離就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實邊個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c582aab352933c73df15ad08bfc0c86982dc0820","tid":122033,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:17:57